description:
WuTility helps you manage your W&T network devices

Management and inventorying tool for W&T network devices. Active search for Web-IO devices, USB Servers, Com-Servers and other W&T network components in the local subnet, display of all important information at a glance. Additional functions are initial assignment of IP addresses, copying of entire configuration blocks, uploading of firmware updates as well as direct telnet and browser access.
